com.sap.spe.condmgnt.finding

Interface IConditionFindingEngine

  • All Known Subinterfaces:
    IFreeGoodsEngine, IPricingEngine

    public interface IConditionFindingEngine
    Interface of a condition finding engine. A condition finding engine is the entry point for the condition finding process. The finding process itself is handled by the condition finding manager.
